snippet.title: Capcom Vs. SNK 2 playthrough (Dreamcast)
snippet.description:
Playthrough of the 3 on 3 mode with Gouki, Ryu and Ryo. I get enough GP points to get one of the true bosses to appear, in this case, Shin Gouki.

The Dreamcast version of Capcom Vs. SNK 2 was only released in Japan.
